headline: America250 Names Leidos First Founding Innovation Partner to Inspire the Next Generation of American Ingenuity
summary: America250, the bipartisan organization charged by Congress to lead the commemoration of the signing of the Declaration of Independence, today announced a landmark partnership with Leidos that will help define how innovation is celebrated throughout the Semiquincentennial.

headline: Leidos Holdings Stock: Analyst Estimates & Ratings
summary: Leidos Holdings has been outperforming the S&P 500 Index over the past year, and analysts remain fairly bullish about the stock’s prospects.
